				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: AE Kiting: Getting that circle started<a name="49032"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 29 04 1:38 PM</span></td>
