				<td colspan="2"><span>Neither is fast enough, you need at least ~130% speed mod in order to be fast enough to <b>autocircle</b>. SoW is around 65% maxed and jboots is flat capped at 50% I think?
<br />

<br />
Selo's is hard capped at 65%(lvl 50). Add a 2.2 mod to that and you will be fast enough to auto-circle.
<br />

<br />
On the flip side, normal AEing is just fine with SoW potions or JBoots, as long as your enemies don't run faster than that. You could even AE kite with just Run3. I never bother with sow potions and such, I usually just do it with run3.</span></td>
